HEADWORD: nonporous
<hw>nonporous</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Not porous; especially, not
having vessels that appear as pores; <as>as, <ex>nonporous</ex>
wood</as>. Opposite of <ant>porous</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

